Effective Date: 22nd September, 2023

Wundrsight Pvt. Ltd. ("Wundrsight," "we," "us," or "our") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use our virtual reality (VR) app called "Rage Room" on the Oculus Quest platform (the "App"). By using the App, you agree to the practices described in this Privacy Policy.

Information We Collect

User-Provided Information: When you use the App, you may provide us with certain information, including but not limited to:

User profile information, such as your username and avatar.
In-app chat and messaging content.
Feedback or reviews submitted through the App.
Automatically Collected Information: We may automatically collect certain information about your use of the App, including:

Device information, including device type, operating system, and device identifier.
Usage data, such as the duration and frequency of your interactions with the App.
Error logs and crash reports.
Location Information: We may collect location information with your consent if the App's features require it. This information may be used for various purposes, such as providing location-based services.

How We Use Your Information

We may use the information we collect for the following purposes:

Providing and Improving the App: We use your information to provide you with access to the App and to improve its functionality and user experience.
Communication: We may use your contact information to send you updates, notifications, and information related to the App, as well as to respond to your inquiries or requests.
Research and Analytics: We may use data to conduct research and analyze user behavior to enhance our services and develop new features.
Legal Compliance: We may use your information as required by applicable laws, regulations, or legal processes, including responding to lawful requests by public authorities.
Protection and Security: We take measures to protect the security and integrity of the App and the information collected, including monitoring for fraudulent or unauthorized activity.
Disclosure of Your Information

We may share your information with third parties in the following circumstances:

Service Providers: We may engage third-party service providers to assist with App development, maintenance, or other operational tasks. These providers are contractually obligated to safeguard your information.
Legal Requirements: We may disclose your information to comply with legal obligations, respond to government requests, or protect our rights, privacy, safety, or property.
Your Choices

You can control how your information is used and shared in the following ways:

Access and Update: You can access and update certain information by logging into your account through the App.
Communication Preferences: You can opt out of receiving promotional emails or notifications from us by following the instructions in those communications.
Deletion of Your Data

If you wish to request the deletion of your collected data, please contact us at raj.gohil@wundrsight.com. We will respond to your request within a reasonable timeframe and take appropriate steps to delete your data in accordance with applicable laws.

Children's Privacy

The App is not intended for children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect or solicit personal information from children under 13. If you believe that a child under 13 has provided us with personal information, please contact us, and we will take appropriate steps to remove such information.

Changes to this Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or for other operational, legal, or regulatory reasons. We will notify you of any material changes through the App or by other means.

Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or our data practices, please contact us at [Insert Contact Information]. By using the App, you consent to the collection, use, and disclosure of your information as described in this Privacy Policy.

